reviewText:
Pros:
- Artwork and visual design;
- Gameplay and storyline that both affects and get affected by the music, this one being a balanced mix between melodic death metal and symphonic music;
- Variety of characters/musical aesthetics;
- Fast and hard-working team that provides feedback to the follower community and bug-fixig;

Cons:
- Mechanics and controls;
- Boring sections of the puzzle platforms;
- Short;
- Association of the concept/character Dissonance" to something bad in music and evil in the world by contrast with the harmony and beauty in the "Melody".

7/10"
